                        <span class="blog-sidebar__dot"></span> UI/UX Design</li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="blog-sidebar__dot"></span> Branding &amp; Identity</li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="blog-sidebar__dot"></span> Illustration</li>
